Package: opera
Type: Package
Title: Online Prediction by Expert Aggregation
Version: 1.2.0
Author: Pierre Gaillard [cre, aut], Yannig Goude [aut], Laurent Plagne
        [ctb], Thibaut Dubois [ctb], Benoit Thieurmel [ctb]
Maintainer: Pierre Gaillard <pierre@gaillard.me>
Copyright: EDF R&D 2012-2015
Description: Misc methods to form online predictions, for
        regression-oriented time-series, by combining a finite set of
        forecasts provided by the user. See Cesa-Bianchi and Lugosi
        (2006) <doi:10.1017/CBO9780511546921> for an overview.
License: LGPL
